          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>
                                        <date>26 feby 5609/<lb/>1849</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>Reverend Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">I have the pleasure to hand you letter<lb/> 4 on
                                        the Union of the congregations. I trust you will not<lb/>
                                        consider me importunate in requesting to be favored
                                        with<lb/> only a few lines in acknowledgment of the receipt
                                        of my now<lb/> three last letters on that subject and if
                                        your occupations<lb/> permit you not to enter at large upon
                                        them that you may<lb/> be able to favor me at least with
                                        noticing their main points<lb/> such as the announcing in
                                        the Occident the time and place<lb/> for holding the
                                        proposed meeting. The 50 copies of my letters<lb/> &amp;c,
                                        by complying with which you will oblige.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">Revd Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Yours very sincerely</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">A A Lindo</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
